Note:
Runa Standard Library Test: Built-in Helper Processes
:End Note

Test "pow works":
    Let result be pow with base as 2 and exponent as 8
    Assert result is equal to 256
    Let result2 be pow with base as 5 and exponent as 0
    Assert result2 is equal to 1
    Let result3 be pow with base as 3 and exponent as 2
    Assert result3 is equal to 9

Test "abs works":
    Assert abs(-10) is equal to 10
    Assert abs(10) is equal to 10
    Assert abs(0) is equal to 0

Test "format_string works":
    Let template be "User {name} is {age} years old"
    Let values be dictionary with:
        "name" as "Alice"
        "age" as 30
    Let formatted be format_string with template as template and values as values
    Assert formatted is equal to "User Alice is 30 years old" 